00:39:00.105 --> 00:39:02.038
- It's just a basketball game...
- Also uncomfortable.

00:39:02.038 --> 00:39:05.372
Uncomfortable? Seriously?
You're making everyone uncomfortable.

00:39:05.372 --> 00:39:07.505
If you don't beat 340 after this,

00:39:07.505 --> 00:39:10.472
it'll be truly awkward.

00:39:10.472 --> 00:39:12.205
Cool.

00:39:13.772 --> 00:39:16.472
- Go for it!
- Let's start.

