00:49:42.338 --> 00:49:44.072
President Han?

00:49:45.805 --> 00:49:48.938
Mr. Lee, it's been a while.

00:49:48.938 --> 00:49:50.405
You've gotten even prettier
since I last saw you.

00:49:50.405 --> 00:49:51.805
Oh, ma'am.

00:49:51.805 --> 00:49:56.438
In a world where practicality rules,
loyalty is old-fashioned.

00:49:56.438 --> 00:49:59.338
Well done. I'm impressed.

00:50:00.305 --> 00:50:01.605
President Han.

00:50:01.605 --> 00:50:03.572
Mr. Lee is mine now.

00:50:03.572 --> 00:50:05.805
What are you doing, getting all clingy now?

00:50:05.805 --> 00:50:07.938
I'm not here to take him away.

00:50:07.938 --> 00:50:10.272
I'm not interested in everyone's sweetheart,

00:50:10.272 --> 00:50:13.638
