your calculation is off.

00:50:17.072 --> 00:50:19.472
Did you underpay a penalty?

00:50:19.472 --> 00:50:21.272
No, no.

00:50:26.338 --> 00:50:28.038
President Han!

00:50:31.905 --> 00:50:34.405
Now, the calculation is a bit more accurate.

00:50:39.072 --> 00:50:40.838
Ugh, my head...

00:50:45.305 --> 00:50:47.038
[Check: One million won]
What is this?

00:50:51.238 --> 00:50:53.905
This woman is ridiculous.

00:50:57.405 --> 00:51:00.438
How can she
just throw the doll away like that?

00:51:01.438 --> 00:51:03.372
That's too much.

00:51:08.933 --> 00:51:10.117
[Si Hyeong]

00:51:11.205 --> 00:51:13.272
- Hey.
- Finally answering.

00:51:13.272 --> 00:51:15.705
I thought something happened to you.

