Okay, I get what you mean.

00:52:11.438 --> 00:52:14.105
Are you sure you have
no plans to get married?

00:52:17.738 --> 00:52:21.005
Your mother keeps worrying about you.

00:52:21.005 --> 00:52:25.238
But you have no intention to do so at all.

00:52:25.238 --> 00:52:26.693
Isn't that right?

00:52:26.693 --> 00:52:28.438
[15 years ago]

