You're acting weird today.
What is it? What are you hiding?

01:00:07.105 --> 01:00:09.872
- It's nothing.
- Got you.

01:00:11.905 --> 01:00:14.438
Mi Ran, let me explain first...

01:00:14.438 --> 01:00:16.405
Did you have a man?

01:00:17.538 --> 01:00:20.772
Last time you said you
liked someone. Is it him?

01:00:22.138 --> 01:00:24.138
Tell me quickly, who is it?

01:00:24.138 --> 01:00:25.472
Who on earth is he?

01:00:25.472 --> 01:00:26.705
Mi Ran, wait a second.

01:00:26.705 --> 01:00:28.905
Well, that's...

01:00:28.905 --> 01:00:30.672
I don't know who it is.

01:00:30.672 --> 01:00:32.838
No, I know who he is.

01:00:32.838 --> 01:00:37.372
But I don't know his name or what he does...

