the gestational sac and yolk sac.

01:00:51.172 --> 01:00:53.872
You should be able to hear
the heartbeat around week seven.

01:00:53.872 --> 01:00:57.138
It might be slightly delayed
depending on your menstrual cycle.

01:00:57.138 --> 01:01:00.838
Shall we schedule your next appointment?

01:01:10.805 --> 01:01:14.338
Even now, you're worried about
seeing someone you know?

01:01:14.338 --> 01:01:16.838
What did the doctor say?
Are you actually pregnant?

01:01:20.272 --> 01:01:22.772
What should I do now?

01:01:22.772 --> 01:01:26.405
What do you mean?
You need to find that man first.

01:01:26.405 --> 01:01:29.672
Don't you remember anything
about the baby's father?

01:01:31.705 --> 01:01:32.872
Well...

01:01:32.872 --> 01:01:35.838
He's about 6'1", maybe?

01:01:35.838 --> 01:01:38.838
He has double eyelids, thick eyebrows.

01:01:38.838 --> 01:01:42.772
He looks chic when not smiling,
but like a puppy when he does.

01:01:42.772 --> 01:01:45.972
You observed him in great detail.

01:01:52.138 --> 01:01:54.772
Could it be him you're talking about?

01:01:55.738 --> 01:01:57.638
Oh? Manager!

01:01:59.005 --> 01:02:00.938
Is she from your company?

01:02:06.438 --> 01:02:10.305
Wait, that necklace...

01:02:11.472 --> 01:02:14.838
He's a bit older, but a total romantic.

01:02:14.838 --> 01:02:16.605
Girlfriend?

01:02:19.438 --> 01:02:20.738
You punk.

01:02:20.738 --> 01:02:22.438
That's her.

01:02:32.472 --> 01:02:33.572
- Se Hyeon.
- What's wrong?

01:02:33.572 --> 01:02:36.405
- Is this the punk you were talking about?
- Manager.

01:02:37.538 --> 01:02:40.405
Who are you? Do you know what you've done?

01:02:40.405 --> 01:02:42.472
Manager, this is my uncle.

01:02:42.472 --> 01:02:44.938
That woman who's been haunting
my thoughts since that day.

01:02:44.938 --> 01:02:45.972
Ms. Jang Hui Won.

01:02:45.972 --> 01:02:49.038
You left the baby's ultrasound photo.

01:03:08.072 --> 01:03:10.805
The woman I was searching for

01:03:11.472 --> 01:03:13.538
now has a baby.

01:03:58.972 --> 01:04:00.172
Am I your baby's father?

01:04:00.172 --> 01:04:01.605
Let's just go our separate ways.

01:04:01.605 --> 01:04:02.638
Are you going to be a father?

01:04:02.638 --> 01:04:04.305
I'm ruined.

01:04:04.305 --> 01:04:06.172
Are you really the Jang Hui Won I know?

01:04:06.172 --> 01:04:08.438
Do you like him? Are you dating him?

01:04:08.438 --> 01:04:10.838
Why is he here?

01:04:10.838 --> 01:04:11.905
Wait a minute.

01:04:11.905 --> 01:04:14.138
Manager Jang Hui Won,
people will misunderstand.

01:04:14.138 --> 01:04:17.938
Ah, you can't do this to me.

01:04:17.938 --> 01:04:20.005
No, this is exactly the kind of situation
that invites misunderstanding.

01:04:20.005 --> 01:04:21.272
Like falling in love at first sight...

01:04:21.272 --> 01:04:22.372
Kang Du Jun?

01:04:22.372 --> 01:04:24.205
[Jang Hui Won]
She's pregnant?

01:04:24.205 --> 01:04:25.605
How amusing.

01:04:25.605 --> 01:04:27.705
Uncle, you're not getting married
because of me, are you?

01:04:27.705 --> 01:04:29.705
I'll take responsibility.

01:04:29.705 --> 01:04:30.738
Let's get married.

01:04:30.738 --> 01:04:32.438
What?